Diagram 1 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black is dead. This is correct.
\par White's placement at 1 is severe.
\par It's the 1-2 vital point.
\par
\par If black plays at 2, it is calm for white to block on the outside with 3.
\par
\par Even if black connects at \b\f1 A\b0\f0 , the black group is still dead.
\par }
