Diagram 2 (Dead?)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It might be easy to mistake white's attachment at 1 for the vital point.
\par
\par If black hanes at 2, white descends at 3 and \b\f1 A\b0\f0  and \b\f1 B\b0\f0  are matbogi.
\par
\par This would indeed leave black's group dead, but black will not play like this.
\par
\par Let's consider black's correct response.
\par }
