\par Black responds to white \'a1\'e2 with a brilliant clamp at 1. Black has grabed the vital point.
\par
\par If white plays at \b\f1 A\b0\f0 , black lives at \b\f1 B\b0\f0 .
\par Of course if white plays at \b\f1 B\b0\f0 , black lives at \b\f1 A\b0\f0 . matbogi.
\par
\par The previous diagram is merely white's fantasy.
\par }
