Diagram 4 (There's Death in a Hane?)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is an attack in accordance with the proverb stating, "There's death in a hane", but in this case black 2 is a calm move and white fails.
\par
\par Black 2 is again the 1-2 vital point.
\par }
